Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:00:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我才会试图跟你交谈\NThat's why I tried to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}格伦告诉我  你救了他的命\NGlenn told me you saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他救了我的命\NHe saved mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们就该这样互相照顾  对吗\NThat's how it works with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去找点吃的\NGet something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}日出时我们动身\NWe'll start back at sunup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟瑞克谈了谈\NTalked to Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些人知道你在监狱\NSome of them know what you did
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}做的事\Nat the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}达里尔  玛姬\NDaryl, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们接受了\NThey accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他们没接受  你不会在这里\NYou wouldn't be here if they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要跟其余人聊聊\NGonna talk to the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他们也接受\NTell them to accept it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们没必要接受\NThey don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  有必要\NNo, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的有必要\NThey just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们没必要告诉他们小女孩的事\NWe don't need to tell them about the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想说\NI don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得忘记那事\NI just need to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就是我们等待时机的原因\NRight there is why we're waiting for our moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  有道理\NYeah, fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感谢你救我一命\NI owe you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你应该感谢泰尔西  他当时在监狱\NYou owe Tyreese. He was at the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你回去了\NYou got back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这在他们的一间储藏室里\NIt was in one of their storerooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看见他们杀了他\NI saw them kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那孩子\NThat kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还是不知道你做了什么\NI still don't know about what you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我知道  你懂一些我不懂的事\NBut I know you knew some things I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我让你独自前行\NI sent you away to this--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说过我能活下来  你说得对\NYou said I could survive. You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我让你独自前行  现在我们加入了你\NI sent you away to this and now we're joining you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你愿意接纳我们吗\NWill you have us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想谈论这事\NI don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我做不到\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得忘记这事\NI just need to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们投降\NWe surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没踪迹  什么也没有\NNo tracks. No nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以不管你昨晚听到了什么...\NSo whatever you heard last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有不祥的预感\NIt's more what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果有人在监视我们\NIf someone was watching us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}应该会发生一些事才对\Nthere would have been something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟紧点\NKeep close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}准备好踏上水泥地了吗\NReady to get some concrete under your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是时候了\NI think it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真是悦耳啊  警官\NThat is sweet music to my ears, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再遇到一条路我们就沿路走\NTake the next road we come to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}继续朝北走直到发现车辆\Ntry to get back to going north till we find a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-好吗  -好\N- Good? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟紧点\NTighten it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}湿袜子\NUh, wet socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}脚凉快\NCool feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}蚊子咬\NMosquito bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}瘙痒让你知道自己还活着\NItching reminds you you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}处处都有危险\NDanger around every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一刻也不无聊\NNever a dull moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}日头毒辣\NThe hot sun beating down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}晒成漂亮的棕色\NCome on, a glorious tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说的是真心话\NI said it and I meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有隐私\NNo privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有忠实的观众\NCaptive audience.
