Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救命啊  救命啊\NHelp! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安全了  注意观察\NWe're clear. Keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}下来吧\NCome on down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我叫加百利\NI'm Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你身上有武器吗\NDo you have any weapons on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看起来像是会有武器的人吗\NDo I look like I would have any weapons?
