Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有任何武器\NI have no weapons of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝之道足以庇护我\NThe word of god is the only protection I need.
