Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里有核桃\NWe've got some pecans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真是个美丽的孩子\NThat's a beautiful child.
