Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有个教堂\NI have a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把手举过头顶\NHold your hands above your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你杀过多少行尸\NHow many walkers have you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-一只也没  -转过去\N- Not any, actually. - Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你杀过多少人\NHow many people have you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没杀过\NNone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为上帝憎恶暴力\NBecause the lord abhors violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你都做过什么\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都做过肮脏的事\NWe've all done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是个罪人\NI'm a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我几乎每天都犯下罪行\NI sin almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我只向上帝忏悔那些罪行\NBut those sins, I confess them to god,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而不是向陌生人\NNot strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说你有个教堂\NYou said you had a church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喂  之前\NHey, earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是你在监视我们吗\NWere you watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只管自己的事\NI keep to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这年头  活人和死人\NNowadays, people are just as dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一样危险  你们觉得呢\NAs the dead, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  人更危险\NNo, people are worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总之我没有监视你们\NWell, I wasn't watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}灾变后  我最远只去过几次\NI haven't been beyond the stream near my church
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}教堂边上的河流\NMore than a few times since it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今天之前  我最远只到过那儿\NThat was the furthest I've gone before today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或许我在说谎\NOr maybe I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许我全是骗你们的\NMaybe I'm lying about everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}前面根本没有什么教堂\Nand there's no church ahead at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许我在把你们带向陷阱\NMaybe I'm leading you into a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以偷走你们的松鼠\Nso I can steal all your squirrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}教区的教徒们常说\NMembers of my flock had often told me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的幽默感令人扶额\Nthat my sense of humor leaves much to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}的确如此\NYeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}圣莎拉教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等\NHold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以让我们先检查一下吗\NCan we take a look around first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们可不想把松鼠拱手送人\NWe just want to hold on to our squirrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}神赐恩宠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}汝不可杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}创世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们行善  不可丧志  若不灰心  到了时候就要收成\N加拉太书  6:9
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迷途40年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在这儿待了好几个月  连大门都没出\NI spent months here without stepping out the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你们发现里面有人\NIf you found someone inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那可就奇了怪了\NWell, it would have been surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢了\NThanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在后院发现一辆小巴士\NWe found a short bus out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但无法发动\NIt don't run,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过我敢说一两天就能修好\Nbut I bet we could fix that in less than a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}神父说他不要那辆车\NFather here says he doesn't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看来我们有交通工具了\NLooks like we found ourselves some transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你清楚现在的当务之急  对吧\NYou understand what's at stake here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我清楚\NYes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}既然现在可以休息...\NNow that we can take a breath--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}休息就要拖慢进度\NWe take a breath, we slow down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拖慢了就要出岔子\NShit inevitably goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不管接下来要干嘛  我们都需要补给\NWe need supplies no matter what we do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说得没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}水  食物  弹药\NWater, food, ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别开那辆车\NShort bus ain't going nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去给你们找些焗豆\NBring you back some baked beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论如何都要跟瑞克步调一致\NOne way or another, we're doing what Rick does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大伙儿别再走散了\NWe're not splitting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听他的\NWhat he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们很想跟你们走  但还是听她的吧\NWe want to roll with you, but... What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你靠什么活了这么久\NHow'd you survive here for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}补给从哪儿来的\NWhere did your supplies come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}靠运气\NLuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}年度罐装食物捐赠活动\NOur annual canned food drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刚刚举行完就出事了\NThings fell apart right after we finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只剩我一个人\NIt was just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来  朱迪思\NCome here, judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我靠那些食物撑了很久\NThe food lasted a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}后来我便四处搜索补给\NAnd then I started scavenging.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把附近的房子都清了一遍\NI've cleaned out every place nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}除了一个地方\NExcept for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么不去那儿\NWhat kept you from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}被行尸占据了\NIt's overrun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有多少\NHow many?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}十多只吧  或许更多\NA dozen or so. Maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们能拿下十多只\NWe can handle a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我和鲍勃跟你去\NBob and I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}泰尔西留下\NTyreese should stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}保护朱迪思\Nhelp keep judith safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以吗\NThat'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}假如你需要我照看她\NYou ever need me to watch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者需要我为她做任何事  我都愿意\Nneed anything for her, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}非常感谢\NI'm grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有谢谢你做的其它一切\NAnd everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我给你们画张地图  -没必要\N- I'll draw you a map. - You don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你和我们一起去\NYou're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我什么忙也帮不上\NI'm not gonna be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们也看见了\NYou saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会对付行尸\NI'm no good around those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你和我们一起去\NYou're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着\NListen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我不信任这个人  -为什么\N- I don't trust this guy.  - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么信任他\NWhy do you trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并非所有人都是坏人\NEverybody can't be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不信任这个人\NI don't trust this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我要带上他\NAnd that's why I'm bringing him with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但他可能有其他同伴\NBut he could have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我需要你时刻警惕\NSo I need you to stay alert
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帮着泰尔西保护朱迪思  好吗\Nand help Tyreese protect Judith, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要你听好了我接下来要说的话\NI need you to hear what I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你并不安全\NYou are not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论你身边有多少人\NNo matter how many people are around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论这里看起来有多安全\Nor how clear the area looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论其他人怎么说\Nno matter what anyone says,
