Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.33,0:29:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我  我慌了\NI-- I panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.85,0:29:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我告诉过你  我...\NI told you I...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.99,0:29:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她活着时是你的熟人吗\NYou knew her when she was alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.18,0:29:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我明白了\NYeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.83,0:29:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你只对上帝坦白罪孽\NYou only tell your sins to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想念你的刀吗\NDo you miss the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.72,0:29:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本来也不是我的\NWasn't really mine in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.46,0:29:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}灾变刚开始时找来的\NFound it, in the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.31,0:29:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你身手为何这么好\NHow'd you get so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.71,0:29:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在外面除了我就是它们\NIt was just me and them out here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.90,0:29:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}日复一日\Nall day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.14,0:29:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}像这样过了很久\NA good long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.81,0:30:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道那是什么  但那不是生活\NI don't know what that was, but it wasn't a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.26,0:30:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不像今天\NNot like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.39,0:30:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在三尺深的污水中举步维艰地寻找食物\NStumbling around in three feet of slime for some peas and carrots,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.20,0:30:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这才叫生活\Nthat's living.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想安德莉亚了\NI miss Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.95,0:30:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也想赫谢尔\NI miss Hershel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.35,0:30:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不怀念在这之前的生活\NI don't miss what was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.02,0:30:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想那把刀\NI don't miss that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.01,0:30:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}泰尔西说你在后面\NTyreese said you were out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.10,0:30:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}进来吧  我们找到食物了\NCome on in. We found food.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.65,0:30:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-有不少呢  -很好\N- A lot of it. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.47,0:30:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是什么\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.36,0:30:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些划痕\NThose scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.91,0:30:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}深深地刻在窗框上\NThey're deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.94,0:30:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好像是有人用刀子划的\NLike knives or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.04,0:30:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人想进去\NSomeone was trying to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.09,0:31:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还找到了一些东西\NI found something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不确定到底发生了什么  但无论什么事\NI don't know what happened, but whatever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.10,0:31:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都可以解决\Nwe can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.82,0:31:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然这不意味着加百利是坏人\NDoesn't mean Gabriel is a bad guy for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.75,0:31:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但它一定意味着什么\Nbut it means something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.85,0:31:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会因此下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.23,0:31:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想祝酒\NI'd like to propose a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我环顾这个房间\NI look around this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.11,0:31:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到了生存者\NAnd I see survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.12,0:31:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在座的每一位\NEach and every one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.95,0:32:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都赢得了这个称号\Nhas earned that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.68,0:32:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-敬生存者  -生存者  干杯\N- To the survivors. - Survivors! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干杯\NCheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.09,0:32:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}生存者\NSurvivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.08,0:32:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们只想当生存者吗\NIs that all you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.17,0:32:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早上醒来\NWake up in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.52,0:32:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}与行尸搏斗  四处觅食\Nfight the undead pricks, forage for food,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.65,0:32:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夜晚也无法安心入睡\Ngo to sleep at night with two eyes open,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.35,0:32:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样周而复始\Nrinse and repeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.14,0:32:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们可以这样做\N'cause you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.73,0:32:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为你们有实力\NI mean, you got the strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.39,0:32:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们也有技能\NYou got the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问题是  对于你们来说\NThing is, for you people,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.79,0:32:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对于你们的能力而言  那只意味着屈服\Nfor what you can do, that's just surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.73,0:32:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们把尤金送到华盛顿  他将消灭行尸\NNow, we get Eugene to Washington and he will make the dead die
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.57,0:32:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让活人重新掌控世界\Nand the living will have this world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.38,0:32:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然路途艰辛 但值得一搏\NAnd that is not a bad takeaway for a little road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.58,0:32:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}尤金  特区有什么\NEugene, what's in DC?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.45,0:33:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们建了个基地  足以应对\NInfrastructure constructed to withstand pandemics
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}时下的瘟疫狂潮\Neven of this fubar magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.93,0:33:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那里有食物  燃料和避难所\NThat means food, fuel, refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.28,0:33:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切重新开始\NRestart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.88,0:33:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论结果怎么样\NHowever this plays out,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.89,0:33:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论花多长时间才能重新开始\Nhowever long it takes for the reset button to kick in,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.62,0:33:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们在那里都会更安全\Nyou can be safe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.52,0:33:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}比灾变后的任一时期都安全\NSafer than you've been since this whole thing started.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.52,0:33:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟我们走吧\NCome with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.08,0:33:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为小家伙拯救世界\NSave the world for that little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.37,0:33:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为你们自己拯救世界\NSave it for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.69,0:33:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为那些在外逃难\NSave it for the people out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}除了生存别无希望的人拯救世界\Nwho don't got nothing left to do except survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.79,0:34:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么了\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想她知道我要说什么\NI think she knows what I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.23,0:34:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她要加入  她加入我就加入\NShe's in. If she's in, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.16,0:34:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我们加入  -太好了\N- We're in. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.05,0:34:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来吧\NLet's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.46,0:34:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.33,0:34:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会让我哥哥\NI'm not letting my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.26,0:34:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}独享抱那孩子的乐趣\Nbe the only one that gets to hold that baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.27,0:34:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.28,0:34:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再来一个\NOne more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.15,0:35:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你还好吗  -挺好的\N- You okay? - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.63,0:35:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去过监狱\NI was at the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.51,0:35:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟总督一起\NWith the Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.11,0:35:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我那时不知道他是谁\NI didn't know who he was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.31,0:35:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会做什么\Nor what he could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.86,0:35:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也不了解你们\NAnd I didn't know who all of you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.42,0:35:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是不想隐瞒\NI-- I just didn't want it to be hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在那里待过\NThat I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.58,0:35:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在跟我们在一起\NYou're here with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.65,0:36:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感谢招待\NThanks for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.96,0:36:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你竟然肯让我们喝你的圣餐酒让我很意外\NI'm surprised you let us drink your communion wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.10,0:36:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有人吃圣餐了\NThere isn't anyone left to take communion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.78,0:36:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没祝福过的酒只是普通的酒罢了\NThe wine's just wine until it's blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.15,0:36:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你一定隐瞒了什么\NYou're hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.93,0:36:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且很显然是你无法逃避的事\NAnd it's pretty obvious it's something you can't hide from.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.01,0:36:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是你的事\NThat's your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.62,0:36:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是这些人\NBut these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.31,0:36:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些人是我的家人\Nthese people are my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.07,0:36:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你隐瞒的事情会伤害到他们\NAnd if what you're hiding somehow hurts them in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.93,0:37:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会杀了你\NI'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.80,0:37:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.71,0:37:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.35,0:37:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.11,0:38:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在干什么  你在干什么\NWhat are you doing? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.98,0:38:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}贝丝在他们手上\NThey got Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.10,0:38:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快点  上车\NCome on. Come on, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.95,0:39:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你醒了吗\NYou waking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.79,0:39:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你醒来了\NAh, you're back with us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.28,0:39:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好消息是\NGood news is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.42,0:39:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还没死\NYou're not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.07,0:39:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}松了一口气  对吗\NThat's a relief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但别高兴的太早\NBut try not to read too much into the word yet there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.17,0:39:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}否则你会疯掉的  鲍勃\NIt'll just drive you crazy, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.67,0:39:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想解释一下自己\NI want to explain myself a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你瞧\NYou see,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.30,0:40:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们刚才并不想\NWe didn't want to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.98,0:40:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伤害你\Nbefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.18,0:40:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不想让你脱离团队  或吓唬你\NWe didn't want to pull you away from your group or scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.36,0:40:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不想这样做\NThese aren't things that we want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.67,0:40:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们只是必须这样做\NThey're things we got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.53,0:40:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你和你的伙伴夺走了我们的家\NYou and your people took away our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.68,0:40:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这很正常\NThat's fair play.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.64,0:40:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在我们像其他人一样\NNow we're out here like everybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.83,0:40:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}试图在外面生存\Ntrying to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了生存\NAnd in order to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.10,0:40:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们必须狩猎\NWe have to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.12,0:40:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最早的时候\NDidn't start that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.20,0:40:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不吃人\Neating people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.57,0:40:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}事情演化成了这样\NIt evolved into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.46,0:40:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们进化了\NWe evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.61,0:40:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不得不\NWe had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.92,0:40:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而现在  我们退化了\NAnd now we've devolved
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}变成了猎人\Ninto hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.77,0:41:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我给你说过\NI told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.63,0:41:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说过回不去了  鲍勃\NI said it. Can't go back, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.75,0:41:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是希望你明白\NI just hope you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.82,0:41:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你身上发生的事不是私人恩怨\Nthat nothing happening to you now is personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.18,0:41:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  是你害我们落到这般境地\NYeah, you put us in this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.11,0:41:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而现在躺在这里的人是你\Nand it is almost kind of a cosmic justice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.12,0:41:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}似乎是某种报应  但是\Nfor it to be you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.89,0:41:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}换做别人我们也会这样做的\NWe would have done this to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.16,0:41:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会的\NWe will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.26,0:41:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是归根结底\NBut at the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.60,0:41:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不管我们多么讨厌这种丑陋的事\NNo matter how much we hate all this ugly business...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.39,0:41:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人总是要吃东西的\NA man's got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.76,0:42:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果能让你感到安慰的话\NIf it makes you feel any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.92,0:42:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的味道比我们想的好多了\NYou taste much better than we thought you would.

